ruleset:

The Padawan Ruleset contains a collection of rules taken from Padawan.


    <rule name="EmptyTry"
          since="0.2.7"
          message="Avoid empty try{} statements"
          class="PHP_PMD_Rule_Padawan_EmptyTry"
          >

TBD.

        3


class Something {
    public static function main( array $as ) {
        try{ // VIOLATION - empty
        } catch (Exception $ex) {
            // do something
        } 
    }
}




    <rule name="EmptyCatch"
          since="0.2.7"
          message="Avoid empty catch() statements"
          class="PHP_PMD_Rule_Padawan_EmptyTry"
          >

TBD.

        3


class Something {
    public static function main( array $as ) {
        try{ 
            $a = $a + 1;
        } catch (Exception $ex) {
            // VIOLATION -empty
        } 
    }
}
